NAME
  CONNECT - Connect to Wi-Fi (Internal)

SYNOPSIS
  CONNECT [ssid] [password]

DESCRIPTION
  Connects to a Wi-Fi network.
  Credentials are saved to wifi.cfg
  for auto-connection on next boot.
  
  If run without arguments, it attempts
  to connect using saved credentials.

EXAMPLES
  CONNECT MyWifi MyPassword
  CONNECT

SEE ALSO
  SETSERVER, GET, PUT